title: Gueye sent off for striking team-mate - but Moyes 'quite likes' it
subtitle: Everton's Idrissa Gueye is sent off for striking team-mate Michael Keane during their Premier League victory at Manchester United.
full_text: Everton's Idrissa Gueye is sent off for striking team-mate Michael Keane during their Premier League victory at Manchester United.
